(345, 1, '2025-05-16 19:58:06', '2025-05-16 19:58:06', '<p class=\"\" data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"1065\">I developed a feature-rich, modern, and fully responsive eCommerce website for <strong data-start=\"806\" data-end=\"822\">MediQ Lasers</strong>, a professional laser equipment provider based in the Netherlands. Built with <strong data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"930\">WordPress and <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\">WooCommerce</a></strong>, this custom-designed site ensures a smooth user experience, streamlined product management, and powerful online shopping functionality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1095\"><strong data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1095\">Project Overview:</strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"197\" data-end=\"494\">MediQ Lasers needed a high-performance and professional website to showcase and sell its advanced laser equipment online. I delivered a complete eCommerce solution using <strong data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"389\">WordPress</strong> and <strong data-start=\"394\" data-end=\"418\">WooCommerce</strong>, with a fully responsive and user-friendly design tailored for conversions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"878\">The project was built using the <strong data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"559\">Divi Page Builder </strong>for flexible layout design and includes dynamic features such as <strong data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"655\">Slider Revolution</strong> for interactive visuals and product sliders. To enhance visibility, I implemented <strong data-start=\"738\" data-end=\"759\">Yoast SEO Premium</strong> for advanced search engine optimization. Live chat support is handled via <strong data-start=\"834\" data-end=\"843\">Tidio</strong> for real-time customer engagement.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"1052\">This tech stack ensures fast performance, mobile compatibility, SEO optimization, and a professional online shopping experience tailored to the client\'s branding and goals.</p>', 'MediQLasers – WooCommerce WordPress Store', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mediqlasers-woocommerce-wordpress-store', '', '', '2025-05-18 05:58:19', '2025-05-18 05:58:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/developersajeeb/src/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=345', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
