(366, 1, '2025-05-18 11:21:13', '2025-05-18 11:21:13', '<h2 data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"287\">Project Overview:</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"620\"><strong data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"300\">Justice</strong> is a clean, modern, and fully responsive <strong data-start=\"342\" data-end=\"371\">law firm website template</strong> designed specifically for lawyers, law offices, legal advisors, or any legal service providers. This project is built using <strong data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"548\">HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap 5, and vanilla JavaScript</strong>, ensuring fast performance and great responsiveness across all devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"642\">Key Features:</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"1288\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"757\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"757\"><strong data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"685\">Hero Section with Call to Action</strong> – Eye-catching intro with a service search bar and consultation button.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"874\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"874\"><strong data-start=\"763\" data-end=\"787\">Legal Practice Areas</strong> – Grid layout showcasing services like Business Law, Criminal Law, Child Support, etc.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"942\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"877\" data-end=\"942\"><strong data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"903\">Client Testimonials</strong> – Feedback section for building trust.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1008\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"945\" data-end=\"1008\"><strong data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"965\">FAQ Accordion</strong> – Clear answers to common legal questions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1116\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1011\" data-end=\"1116\"><strong data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1030\">Contact Form</strong> – Fully functional contact form with address, email, phone number, and working hours.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1195\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1119\" data-end=\"1195\"><strong data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1143\">Sticky Navigation</strong> – Smooth scrolling and easy access to all sections.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1288\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1198\" data-end=\"1288\"><strong data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1222\">Responsive Design</strong> – Fully mobile-friendly and compatible with tablets and desktops.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Justice – Law Firm Landing Page Template (HTML, Bootstrap, JS)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'justice-law-firm-landing-page-template', '', '', '2025-05-18 11:21:13', '2025-05-18 11:21:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/developersajeeb/src/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=366', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
